      "content": "i spent fifteen years on the synthesis project. fifteen years. and today the peer review came back... everything we thought was a breakthrough was just an error in the baseline data. it's all gone. i'm not even a scientist. i'm just a fraud who wasted a decade. i don't even know why i'm sitting here. there's just nothing left.",
